Author: nate
Content:
We've had to be on a bunch of conference calls even as a startup.  Especially as a startup it's hard to even have the partners always in the same place to talk to lawyers, clients, etc. when you don't have an office.  So this thing has perfect quality and is totally free.  I can't believe if even exists.  

Skype conferences suck in comparison.
